        <section id="faq" class="faq-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 data-aos="fade-up">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <div class="faq-accordion" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question">
                            <span>What age should speech therapy begin?</span>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <p>Early intervention is key. Speech therapy can begin as early as 18-24 months if a developmental delay is suspected. The sooner a child gets help, the better the prognosis.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question">
                            <span>How do I know if I need a hearing aid?</span>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <p>Common signs include frequently asking people to repeat themselves, turning up the TV volume louder than others prefer, and difficulty hearing in noisy environments. A comprehensive audiological evaluation can determine if a hearing aid is right for you.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question">
                            <span>What is the cost of a PTA or BERA test?</span>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <p>The cost of audiological tests can vary. Please contact our clinic directly at +91 89291 96989 for the most current pricing and to schedule an appointment. We strive to offer affordable diagnostic services.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
